00:39:55.240 --> 00:39:57.400
[Amit Varma]: you know, two consenting adults in their bedroom,

00:39:57.400 --> 00:39:59.560
[Amit Varma]: they can do whatever they want in our daily interactions.

00:39:59.560 --> 00:40:03.800
[Amit Varma]: We can do whatever they want, but when it comes to trade, suddenly we,

00:40:03.800 --> 00:40:07.520
[Amit Varma]: we come up with all these fallacious theories and we say that, no,

00:40:07.520 --> 00:40:09.200
[Amit Varma]: we should interfere. And no,

00:40:09.200 --> 00:40:11.680
[Amit Varma]: I think if it is immoral in the first case to interfere,

00:40:11.680 --> 00:40:13.600
[Amit Varma]: it is immoral in every case to interfere.

00:40:13.600 --> 00:40:17.720
[Amit Varma]: If you're consenting adults interact with each other because both of them

00:40:17.720 --> 00:40:20.200
[Amit Varma]: benefit, uh, in various ways,

